{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述血果情深的故事。七妙神君梅山民在五华山高歌，回忆往事。随后场景转到长安城，老王与小余对话，介绍兰姑（阿兰）教小余认字读书。兰姑回忆自己与大哥（吴凌风）的往事，包括被金大人救起、与苏蕙芷的误会等。苏蕙芷来访，向阿兰解释吴凌风一直在寻找她。吴凌风来到长安找到阿兰，两人重逢，吴凌风用血果汁和万年灵泉治愈阿兰的眼睛，使她重见光明。本章展现了阿兰与吴凌风的深厚感情，以及阿兰从绝望到重获希望的心路历程。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对酒当歌，人生几何？譬如朝露，去日苦多，慨当以慷，忧思难忘……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨儿夜里这场大雪，只怕是交春来最大的一回哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再过一会儿，等到大家都起身出门，这样滑的路，就是平日不雇车儿的人，也只有光顾我老王了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小余，难怪一个多月不见你啦，原来你竟跑到林大爷家去了，喂！你晚上怎地也不来推牌九了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "王大哥，我再不赌了，现在我可忙得很，每晚兰姑都要教我认字读书。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "倒瞧不出你小余，这大年纪了竟还读书认字，难道还想中状元不成？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "我以前也只道咱们穷人，除了靠卖劳力混饭吃，那还能干什么，可是自从兰姑教我识字念书以来，这种想法可有了改变。兰姑说穷人也是人，为什么别人能做的事，咱们便不能做？你别笑我年纪太大，兰姑说宋朝有个姓苏的大学问家，从廿几岁，才开始读书哩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我可不与你争辩，那兰姑我只知道她手艺巧妙，想不到竟还是个知书识礼的女学士哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lao_wang",
      "text": "兰姑可懂得多哩，你没吃过她烧的菜，那可真是好吃极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_wang",
      "speaker_name": "老王",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "她和方婆婆原来就住在我家后面，她那手刺绣，我活到这么大，也还没有见过第二个人有这能耐，不要说她是瞎子，就是'亮子'，谁能赶得上她呢？唉！这么好的一个姑娘。小余，唉，你们老爷……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小余！小余！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这么冷，大清早只穿两件夹衣，着了凉怎么办？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑，老爷后天可要回来了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "乘他还没回来，我们待会儿到牢里去瞧瞧方婆婆。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "方婆婆已经走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "她几时被放走的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "前几天，我遇到狱卒老李，他告诉我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！她一个人年纪那么大，能走到哪去呢？是我害了她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "那怎能怪你！那些捕头儿，就只会欺侮老弱穷人，哼，真正的飞贼大盗，他们可连影儿也碰不到。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小余，你以后快别再说，被老爷听见了，可不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "哼！我可不怕，大不了被他们抓去杀头。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "好，你不听话，我是为你好呀！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑，您别生气，我以后再也不说啦！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "这才是好孩子。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "门旁兰花又开了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "不但兰花开了，梅花也开了，对了，我摘几枝来插花瓶。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "好生生开在树上，不要去摘它，那香气好闻极啦，我要走近去嗅嗅。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑娘！兰姑娘！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "咱们陕西新巡抚金大人的小姐，她在叫你哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑娘，你当真不认得我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "text": "原来是苏大小姐，民女家中陈设简陋，是以不敢接待芳驾。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑娘，你还生我气？你知道你吴大哥现在在什么地方？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "text": "他难道不是和你在一起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你吴大哥正在天涯海角地寻你呢！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "text": "你说的可是真的吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑娘，不，我叫你兰妹妹好吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "那天你负气一走，次晨吴大哥一知此事，便如失魂落魄，他迫不及待地就和我告别，也不知他到哪里去找你了。兰妹，当真，吴大哥就只喜欢你一人，你……你真有福气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰妹，不瞒你说，我……我原是很喜欢……很喜欢吴大哥的，可是我真笨，我一直以为他喜欢我，到现在我才明白，原来他心中只有你一个人，那日酒醉，他误认我是你，是以造成误会，兰妹，他用情真专，有这样英俊的少年，专心一意地爱你，你真幸福，我……我也替你高兴。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰妹，你怎么啦！你哪儿不舒服？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "text": "苏姐姐，我。一时头晕，所以支持不住。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_hui_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "苏蕙芷",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你先进屋休息，我也要走了，今晚长安城的缙绅替我义父接风，我也要去，改天再来看你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "我要好好睡一觉，你可别来打扰。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小余",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑，你可千万别气苦。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "小余，你别瞎想，我有什么好气的！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑娘可在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，我……我……总算找……找到你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥你终于来了，你终于来了；我天天盼望着你，你终于找来了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，快别哭了，快擦干眼泪，咱们应该欢喜才对呢！你真的别哭了，我有样东西送你，你一定高兴。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，你这大半年到了些什么地方，伯父的仇报了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "我这半年多的经历真是又惊险，又有趣，待日后有空我再慢慢讲给你听，我包你爱听。就在差不多一个月前，我和捷弟在五华山，以二敌四，杀得四大门派掌门人落花流水，那武当派赤阳道人、崆峒厉鹗都被我们杀了，当年，他们四人联手以此阵式害了爹爹，哼，他们没想到在十多年后，会丧生在这阵法上吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，杀得好。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，大娘呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "妈多半被大水冲走了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，那一定没事的，老天爷永远是帮好人的，大娘一定会转危为安。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，你猜我送你的是什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "我猜不着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你现在最希望的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "只要妈和你安好，我还希望什么呢？老天爷都是小气的，我要求太多了，反而失望得厉害。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，我说过要替你找到血果，使你双目复明，总算皇天不负苦心人，竟让我找着了。来，我替你医治。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "咱们先谈谈别的事情，别忙医治。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "朱夫子说过，只要把血果汁服下，静息三个时辰便见功效，何况现在又有万年灵泉，可以先把眼内被毒所浸烂的肌肉复原，阿兰，你先吃下这瓶血果汁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "过三个时辰，当我把布拆开时，你便可以重见光明了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，谢谢你啦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰，你这就去休息。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "不，大哥！我要听你讲故事。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "现在，苦难已经过去了，仇也报了，阿兰，咱们回家去，种田栽花，永远在一起，再也不要分离了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "咱们先找到大娘，我可要好好报答她老人家，家乡的房子一定被大水冲走了，那也好，我们就搬到泰山脚下，在那里盖一栋房子，这样我们便可常常去看云爷爷。阿兰，那云爷爷喜欢你得很，他再三叮嘱我要带你去见他哩！啊！对了，他住的那儿枣子真好，又大又甜，你一定喜欢吃。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你有什么感觉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "我眼睛痒得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "成了，成了，想不到这灵药功效真快，阿兰，沉住气，我来替你解开。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "阿兰怎么了？怎么了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你可看得见我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，你把我放下来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "你瞧我真乐昏啦，对，阿兰，你双目初愈，不能久用目力，你赶快到床上去睡一觉。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "我等会再来看你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "阿兰",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "大哥，你别离开我。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    }
